{
  "stem": "21308.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We realized only too well that the sooner we met the Russians, the better it would be because that would finish it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- it was just one more thing in a lot of dreadful things which were going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they were dreadful things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was millions of people milling around the place, slave labor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew slave labor had been raised all over the continent and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --but I don't think I can really say more than that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It would have been a-- I really don't honestly think one can say more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was one of a whole lot of things which put together-- together with the camps which we'd now just seen and the Americans had seen-- the sooner the thing is finished, the better it would be.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody was anxious to get the thing finished, but mind you also anxious to try and stay alive, which is not unreasonable.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were professional soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not mercenaries, we were professional soldiers, and we fought very hard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had Jewish people with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But again, I come back to this, they were German Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had various Jews with us who were Germans who were fighting with us in British uniform with British names to camouflage and protect them in case they were taken prisoner.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can remember two or three of them now, their names.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't know what-- never did know what their Jewish name was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One was named Lane, he was in an Hungarian Jew and he married-- he married a member of the Rothschild family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew another one who was a German Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
